<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Micah on Christian Internet Resources</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/</link><description>Recent content in Micah on Christian Internet Resources</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Micah 1</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-01/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-01/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="micah-chapter-1">Micah Chapter 1&lt;/h2>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpFirst" style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:1.0in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>A Message from the L&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> to Micah from Moresheth&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:1.0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>       at &lt;b>the Time of Jotham, Ahaz, &lt;i>and&lt;/i> Hezekiah, Kings of Judah.&lt;/b> &lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:1.5in;'>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>What He Saw About Samaria and Jerusalem&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="judgment-against-samaria-and-jerusalem">Judgment Against Samaria and Jerusalem&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;a name="_Hlk122903339">&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;/a>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Listen, every nation;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      listen, world and everybody in it.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Let the Lord G&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: "Times New Roman",serif'>OD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height: 115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> testify against you from his holy Temple.&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Micah 2</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-02/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-02/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="micah-chapter-2">Micah Chapter 2&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="judgment-against-wealthy-oppressors">Judgment Against Wealthy Oppressors&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Misfortune awaits those who devise sin,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  who lie awake plotting schemes in bed!&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      In the morning they do them&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  because they can.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>They covet fields and seize them;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  &lt;i>they desire &lt;/i>horses and take them.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      They rob people &lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  and confiscate the property they’ve inherited.&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Micah 3</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-03/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-03/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="micah-chapter-3">Micah Chapter 3&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="judgment-against-israels-leaders">Judgment Against Israel’s Leaders&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>I said,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      &lt;b>“Listen, leaders of Jacob, rulers of Israel.&lt;/b>&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      Aren’t you supposed to know what’s good,&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;b>&lt;sup>&lt;span style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  2&lt;/span>&lt;/sup>&lt;/b>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>you that hate good and love evil,                                      &lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                              who skin my people alive,&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                              pull the meat off their bones,&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;a name="_Hlk122903789">&lt;b>&lt;sup>&lt;span style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                                             3&lt;/span>&lt;/sup>&lt;/b>&lt;/a>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>eat their flesh,&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Micah 4</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-04/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-04/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="micah-chapter-4">Micah Chapter 4&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="the-mountain-of-the-lord">The Mountain of the LORD&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>In the last days,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      the mountain the L&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: "Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height: 115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>’s Temple’s on&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  will be the tallest mountain.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>It will loom above the hills,&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      and the people from many nations will stream to it.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>They’ll say,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      &lt;i>“Let’s go up to the L&lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>’s mountain,&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Micah 5</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-05/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-05/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="micah-chapter-5">Micah Chapter 5&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="a-promised-ruler-from-bethlehem">A Promised Ruler from Bethlehem&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;a name="_Hlk122904273">&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;/a>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“Muster your troops, &lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Jerusalem&lt;i>; &lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      your enemies are laying siege against you;&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      they’ll hit Israel’s leader in the face with a rod.&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>But you, Bethlehem Ephrathah,&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      though you’re small among Judah’s clans,&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      you’ll have a ruler come out of you on my behalf in Israel.&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Micah 6</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-06/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-06/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="micah-chapter-6">Micah Chapter 6&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="the-lords-case-against-israel">The LORD’s Case Against Israel&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;a name="_Hlk122904611">&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;/a>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Listen to what the L&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: "Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height: 115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> says:&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            &lt;i>“Present to the mountains &lt;/i>your case against me&lt;i>;&lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            let the hills hear your complaint.”&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;b>&lt;sup>&lt;span style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>         2&lt;/span>&lt;/sup>&lt;/b>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>But then &lt;i>listen, mountains, to the L&lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;i>&lt;u>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>’s&lt;/span>&lt;/u>&lt;/i>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> complaint,&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            you enduring foundations of the world.&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Micah 7</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-07/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/micah/chapter-07/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="micah-chapter-7">Micah Chapter 7&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="israels-misery-turned-to-hope">Israel’s Misery Turned to Hope&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Misfortune is waiting for me!&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      I feel like people that pick fruit and gather grapes&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  but have no clusters to eat &lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  or first-ripe figs to satisfy their hunger.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Godly people have disappeared;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  there aren’t any good ones left.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.75in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      They all premeditate murder;&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>